Blockchain Baccarat menjadi cara permainan Baccarat tercepat yang pertama, game ini terjamin jujur dan adil, semoga Anda dapat bertaruh dengan gembira.

Teknologi Blockchain adalah solusi teknis yang tidak bergantung pada pihak ketiga untuk menyimpan, memverifikasi, mengirim dan pertukaran data jaringan melalui sistem node terdesentralisasi dan ini terbuka secara umum untuk seluruh publik dalam jaringan.
Ketika ada lebih dari 6 node yang mengkonfirmasi, maka operasi transaksi tsb tidak dapat dibalik, dan mencapai efek bahwa informasi tidak dapat dimodifikasi.
Setiap kali shoe kartu baru keluar, semua hasil game telah ditentukan, jadi Anda tidak perlu melakukan pemotongan kartu untuk bermain.

Ketika shoe kartu keluar, informasi shoe kartu dienkripsi dan diunggah ke blockchain. Ketika shoe kartu berakhir, sistem akan mengunggah kunci enkripsi ke blockchain untuk membuka kunci informasi kartu, dan pemain dapat periksa informasi kartu di blockchain.
Karena sifat blockchain yang tidak dapat diubah, pemain dapat memverifikasi apakah informasi kartu sama dengan kartu ketika dalam game, sehingga dapat mencapai nol kecurangan.

Game kartu Bull Bull dapat dimainkan oleh banyak orang secara bersamaan, dengan menggunakan 52 lembar kartu poker (tidak termasuk dua lembar kartu joker), urutan pembagian kartu setiap ronde dihasilkan secara acak, dan urutan kartu ditentukan oleh nilai nominal kartu pertama. Dan 5 lembar kartu akan dibagiakn secara merata kepada para pemain. Setelah pemain mendapatkan kartu, maka akan di atur grup sesuai dengan aturan permainan yang telah ditentukan. Banker dan Player akan sesuai dengan urutan membandingkan besar kecil untuk menentukan pemenang dari permainan.

Para tamu memilih player No. 1, No. 2, atau No. 3 untuk memasang taruhan, tamu dapat bertaruh dengan nilai setara atau dua kali lipat dari taruhan player. Ketika memasang taruhan lipat ganda, tamu harus memiliki uang yang cukup untuk memasang taruhan.

Ketika memasang taruhan dengan nilai setara, perbandingan pembayaran adalah 1: 0,97.
 Jika jumlah poinnya sama, maka akan dipilih 1 kartu dengan nilai tertinggi diantara 5 kartu yang ada, dan pihak dengan nilai kartu tertinggi akan menang. Jika jumlah poin dan nilai kartu sama, maka akan dipilih lambang kartu paling besar.

Desainnya berasal dari game klasik kasino - Money Wheel, mirip dengan mesin slot dan gampang dimainkan, diintegrasikan dengan gameplay yang memiliki rate pembayaran kelipatan tinggi, seperti hipnotis yang menciptakan suasana kasino dan sangat seru. Mari kita bersama-sama mendambakan seorang wanita cantik yang membantu Anda memutarkan keberuntungan kemenangan Anda yang ajaib dan besar.

Wheel memiliki 54 posisi berukuran sama, 52 di antaranya berada pada 6 area Main Bet (1, 2, 5, 10, 20, 40), jika Wheel berhenti di area Main Bet tempat pemain bertaruh, maka akan mendapatkan Kemenangan 2 posisi lainnya adalah 2X dan 8X, merupakan indeks multiplier, dapat digunakan sebagai bonus khusus untuk mengalikan nilai kemenangan.
※Harap perhatikan: Jumlah maksimum pembayaran kemenangan akan bervariasi tergantung pada setting operator.
Ketika pemain memasuki game, jika putaran sedang berlangsung, harap tunggu putaran berikutnya untuk mulai memasang taruhan.
Ketika putaran membuka pemasangan taruhan, pemain dapat mulai memilih chip untuk bertaruh secara terpisah di 6 area Main Bet dan 3 Side Bet.
Setelah selesai memasang bet apa pun, perlu mengklik tombol konfirmasi sekali lagi, agar pemasangan bet efektif.
Setelah waktu taruhan berakhir, tidak akan menerima taruhan apapun lagi dan dealer memutar Wheel.
◆Jika hasil putaran berhenti di 6 area Main Bet (1, 2, 5, 10, 20, 40), maka permainan berakhir:
1. Taruhan yang dipasang di area Main Bet dibayar sesuai dengan basic rate hasil kemenangan.
Contoh: hasil kemenangan 5, berarti rate pembayaran 1 : 5, hasil kemenangan 10, berarti rate pembayaran 1 : 10, dan seterusnya.
2. Taruhan yang dipasang di area Side Bet dibayarkan sesuai dengan rate pembayaran ganjil, genap atau indeks multiplier dari hasil putaran.
Contoh: hasil kemenangan adalah ganjil, berarti rate pembayaran 1 : 0,75; hasil kemenangan adalah genap, berarti rate pembayaran 1 : 1,25.

◆Jika hasil putaran berhenti pada Multiplier (2X atau 8X), permainan tidak dianggap berakhir, semua taruhan chip di area Main Bet akan di hold, dan chip di area Side Bet akan dibersihkan, tidak diizinkan untuk memasang taruhan baru.
1. Putar roda lagi dan bila hasilnya adalah 1, 2, 5, 10, 20 atau 40 maka kalikan rate kemenangan normal pada area Main Bet dengan 2 atau 8 sesuai dengan indeks multiplier yang diperoleh sebelumnya.
Contoh: putaran pertama berhenti di 8X, putaran berikutnya berhenti di area taruhan 5, maka pemain yang bertaruh pada area taruhan 5 sebelum chip di hold akan memperoleh (1:5) X 8 = (1:40)

◆Jika hasil dari putaran beberapa kali berhenti pada indeks multiplier (2X atau 8X), permainan tidak akan dianggap berakhir, semua taruhan yang dipasang di area Main Bet akan terus di hold, tidak diizinkan untuk memasang taruhan baru.

1. Pada saat ini akan dilakukan akumulasi multiplier, yaitu, setelah rate pembayaran kemenangan biasa di area Main Bet sebelumnya dikalikan 2 atau 8, dikalikan sekali lagi dengan indeks multiplier baru (2X atau 8X).

2. Akumulasi multiplier akan berlanjut hingga putaran berhenti di salah satu area Main Bet: 1, 2, 5, 10, 20 atau 40. (Contoh, jika Wheel berhenti di 8X, kemudian berhenti di 2X pada putaran berikutnya, dan kemudian berhenti di area taruhan 5, maka pemain yang bertaruh di area taruhan 5 sebelum chip di hold akan memperoleh (1: 5) X 8 X 2 = ( 1:40) X 2 = 1: 80)
Nilai multiplier yang ditampilkan setelah akumulasi multiplier terus-menerus tidak terikat oleh angka dasar yang dipublikasikan dalam tabel pembayaran.
Dalam setiap ronde game, jumlah pembayaran maksimum single bet terbatas. Untuk lebih jelas silakan lihat angka yang diumumkan di bawah statistik bet.
3 Side Bet berupa: ganjil, genap atau multiplier. Pemain tidak diharuskan bertaruh di area Main Bet, dapat juga memasang di area Side Bet secara langsung.
Hasil dari kemenangan Ganjil pada Side Bet sbb: 1 atau 5.
Hasil dari kemenangan Genap pada Side Bet sbb: 2 atau 10 atau 20 atau 40.
Hasil dari kemenangan Multiplier pada Side Bet sbb: dikalikan 2X atau dikalikan 8X
Bila hasil putaran adalah indeks multiplier, maka pemain akan segera kehilangan taruhan pada Ganjil dan Genap.
※Harap perhatikan, jika hasil dari beberapa spin berturut-turut adalah indeks multiplier, bonus indeks multiplier hanya dapat diperoleh satu kali.

Each player is dealt 1 card face up in order from seat 1 to seat 7. The dealer receives their card last, which is face up as well.

The second card is dealt to each player face up in the same order. The dealing phase is complete once all players receive their second cards. (Before the dealer receives their second card, they must wait until all players have finished their turns.)
After all initial cards have been dealt, each player is given the opportunity to increase the points of their hands.
The order is the same as the initial card dealing. On a player's turn, they may choose to stand (receive no more cards) or hit (ask for 1 or more cards).
If the player chooses to stand, their turn ends and the final number of points is calculated based on the cards in the player's hand.
If the hand exceeds 21 points, the hand is called a bust, and the player loses the bet immediately. Otherwise, the player's bet is settled when the dealer's hand is completed.

If the dealer's first card is an Ace of any suit, only the insurance bet option will be available to the player after the second card is dealt. The game will continue regardless of whether the player buys insurance, which will be settled during the dealer’s drawing phase.
If the initial two cards add up to 21 points, it is called a blackjack. You cannot hit when you have 21 points. The dealer draws their second card after all players have completed their actions.

If the dealer's hand is a blackjack, an insurance bonus is awarded to the player who purchased insurance; if a player’s hand is a blackjack as well, it is deemed a tie. Players who do not have a hand with a blackjack lose the round.
If the dealer does not have a blackjack, players who bought insurance lose their insurance bet. Afterward, the dealer stands or hits based on the drawing strategy.
If the dealer's hand exceeds 21, the hand is called a bust, and all players who have not busted win.

If the dealer's stands without a bust, each player's hand is compared to the dealer's. If a player's hand is closer to a 21 than the dealer's, the player wins. If the dealer is closer, the player loses. If the player and dealer have the same number of points, it is a tie (and a draw).
After all bets have been settled, the dealer announces the start of the next round of betting.
The game is played with a total of 7 player seats as well as 1 dealer seat, using a total of 8 decks of cards.
J, Q, and K count as 10 points. Aces count as 1 or 11 points, and other cards are counted according to the number on the card.
After a player stands, hands containing 1 or more Aces are counted at their maximum value, provided they do not exceed 21 points.
If a blue card appears in the round, the deck will be reshuffled for the next round.
When the player's turn runs out of time, the system will automatically draw for the player's hand according to the drawing strategy.
If a player's hand has 11 points or less, the system will automatically choose hit for the player.
If the number of points in the player's hand is higher than 11, the system will consider the hand to be suspended automatically.
The rules for dealers drawing differ from those of the player
Dealers hit when their hand is 16 or less.
They stand when the count is 17 or higher.
A soft hand is one in which the Aces can be counted as either 1 or 11, and the hand never exceeds 21. A hard hand is one in which all the Aces can be counted as only 1 to avoid a hand exceeding 21.

When the initial two cards have a total of 21 points, it is called a blackjack (which is not counted after the Aces have been split) and is paid out at 3 to 2 (stake) as long as the dealer does not have a blackjack.
If both the player and dealer have blackjacks, it is a tie.
Blackjack wins over a hand of 21 points consisting of 3 or more cards.
All other winning bets pay out at 1 to 1.
Dealer and player hands with the same points are deemed ties with no winners or losers.
A hand with more than 21 points is a bust, and if both the player and dealer bust, it is a tie.

Players are not allowed to leave the table if they have already placed a bet; they must wait until the break at the end of the round before they can click the "Back to lobby" button to leave the table.
After each hand is dealt, players can choose to "surrender"; if a player chooses to surrender, their round ends and they lose half of their bet.
If the dealer's initial first card is an Ace, only the insurance bet option is available to the player after the second card is dealt.

If a player chooses to buy insurance, they pay half the amount of their bet as insurance. and the dealer then checks to see if the player has any insurance. The dealer receives their second card after all players complete their actions.
If the second card is a J, Q, K, or 10, the player wins 2x the insurance bet.
If the second card is not a J, Q, K, or 10, the player loses the insurance bet.
If the player chooses not to buy insurance, the game continues.
Even if the player gets a blackjack, they can still buy insurance.
When dealt with a pair of cards of the same value, it can be split into two hands, each with the same stake as the original wager.
If a hand is split, each hand that is split automatically receives a second card.
Players may then stand or hit for 1 or more cards to improve each hand.
After the player chooses to stand for their first hand, they may choose to stand or hit for the second hand.
If splitting Aces, each hand will only receive 1 card. There is no option to hit or double down.
In addition, if a hand with two cards equals 21 points after splitting Aces, this does not count as a blackjack and cannot beat the dealer's blackjack.
Split hands cannot be split again.

To win the game, the player must have a hand that is larger than the dealer's but does not exceed 21 points. The player does not need to consider the hands of other players and only compares their points with the dealer's.
1. Players must confirm their bets within the specified betting period.
2. Once the betting period ends, the first card is dealt clockwise from the first player on the left of the dealer. The first card is dealt face up to each player.
3. Lastly, the dealer gives 1 card face up to themselves.
4. Next, the second card is dealt to each player also face up.
5. The dealer then asks each player to take actions until they stand before moving on to the next player.
6. When all players have completed their actions, the dealer draws their own second card. The dealer must stop at 17 or more points and draw until they are over 16.
7. If your points are closer to 21 than the dealer's, or if the dealer busts, the player is deemed the winner.
8. If your hand is equal in value to the dealer's, the result is a tie.
9. The dealer recycles the used cards.

1. Surrender: After the dealer finishes dealing cards, players receive a chance to surrender. They may decide to surrender based on the value of their hand, in which case they will lose half of their bet.
2. Insurance: If the dealer's first card is an ace, players get a chance to buy insurance after the surrendering period. Players can use half of their initial bet amount to purchase insurance.
If the dealer gets a blackjack, the insured player wins the insurance bet.
If the dealer's hand is not a blackjack, the player loses the insurance money.
Side-betting players do not get insurance along with the participating player.
3. Hit: Players decide whether to hit based on their hand. The dealer provides one face-up card at a time until the player chooses to stand, or when their hand reaches or exceeds 21 points.
4. Double: Players may choose to double their bet but will have to draw one more and only one more card afterwards. Players cannot double their bets after splitting their cards.
5. Splitting: When a player's initial two cards are of the same value, they may split their cards into two separate hands. The bet amount for each hand is the same as the original wager.
After the player chooses to split, the dealer deals cards to the player's first hand on their right.
The dealer asks the player if they want to hit or stand for the right hand.
After finishing the actions for the first hand on the right, the dealer moves on to the second hand on the left, asking the player if they want to hit or stand.
Splitting is not allowed after doubling down.
If the player has a pair of aces, they can only hit once per hand afterwards.
Splitting cards can only be done once, and the dealer must deal a card afterwards.
Only seated players can choose to split.
If the player gets a 10-point card after splitting aces, the hand is not considered as a blackjack and is settled as a normal 21.
6. Stand: Choose not to receive any more cards and compare your current hand with the dealer's.
If a player exceeds the time limit for their turn and has not busted, the dealer will deal the player a card until their hand is greater than 11 points.

1. Unseated players can place side bets for all seats.

Buy Insurance: Side better does not buy insurance with the player.
Double: Side better can choose whether to double.
Split: Side better can choose whether to split. The system will settle bets based on the first hand by default.
